properties.areaDesc: Southeast Pinal County including Kearny/Mammoth/Oracle; Eastern Cochise County Below 5000 Feet including Douglas/Willcox; Upper Gila River and Aravaipa Valleys including Clifton/Safford
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 17 at 4:10AM MST until January 17 at 9:00AM MST by NWS Tucson AZ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Visibility reduced to one quarter mile or less in dense
fog.

* WHERE...Southeast Pinal County, Eastern Cochise County below
5000 feet and Upper Gila River Valley.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM MST this morning.

* IMPACTS...Hazardous driving conditions due to low visibility.
properties.instruction:
If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM MST THIS MORNING
